# Clean Exposure-Only Forecasting Script | Direct + Aux Exposure/Demand Occ + Horizon Block Heads
# Target:
#   Predict future total_dph / buy_box_dph / in_stock_dph
#
# No demand model.
# No NB head.
# No ENN / z.
